OL,7,FA van driver killed another motorist
OL,8,Fwhen he deliberately drove at him
OL,9,Fafter they clashed in a "road rage"
OL,10,Fargument, a jury has heard.
OL,12,FAndrew Robson, 33, is said to have
OL,13,Fintentionally driven his Ford Transit
OL,14,Fvan into Paul Bowles, 50, and knocked
OL,15,Fhim to the ground before driving off.
OL,17,FShortly before, the men had got out of
OL,18,Ftheir vehicles as they stopped at
OL,19,Ftraffic lights in Oldham, at around
OL,20,F6:40pm on 26 March.
