OL,7,FGordon Cole KC, prosecuting, said Mr
OL,8,FBowles was driving was driving home
OL,9,Fwith his daughter, 19, on Broadway,
OL,10,FChadderton, when they noticed a white
OL,11,Fvan driving "very close" to their
OL,12,FNissan Qashqai.
OL,14,FHe said: "It looks as though an
OL,15,Fargument developed, sometimes referred
OL,16,Fto as road rage, and that argument
OL,17,Fresulted in both Mr Bowles and Andrew
OL,18,FRobson getting out of their vehicles
OL,19,Fand there being a fight.
