OL,7,F"That fight stopped and the defendant
OL,8,Fgot back into his van, but before Mr
OL,9,FBowles could get back into his
OL,10,Fvehicle, we say Andrew Robson then
OL,11,Fdeliberately drove his van, swerving
OL,12,Fin the direction of Paul Bowles, and
OL,13,Fdeliberately hit him.
OL,15,F"Not too long after that he made
OL,16,Farrangements for someone to collect
OL,17,Fthe van, which was loaded on to a
OL,18,Ftrailer and it has disappeared. That
OL,19,Fvan has never been recovered."
