OL,7,FEmergency services attended but Mr
OL,8,FBowles died at the scene.
OL,10,FRobson handed himself into police
OL,11,Fshortly before 11pm and gave no
OL,12,Fcomment when interviewed.
OL,14,FMr Cole told jurors an accident
OL,15,Freconstruction expert had examined the
OL,16,Fscene and had concluded there would
OL,17,Fhave been "ample opportunity" for the
OL,18,Fdefendant to have seen Paul Bowles and
OL,19,Fthe swerving towards him was a
OL,20,Fdeliberate act.
