OL,7,FMr Cole went on: "We anticipate that
OL,8,FAndrew Robson is going to say that he
OL,9,Fdid not deliberately drive his van at
OL,10,FPaul Bowles.
OL,12,F"We anticipate he is going to say
OL,13,Ftherefore that he did not intend to
OL,14,Feither kill him or inflict really
OL,15,Fserious harm
OL,17,F"And we anticipate he is likely to say
OL,18,Fthat he did not actually know that he
OL,19,Fcollided with and hit Paul Bowles."
